videos.headline: Montana scores on pick-six
videos.description: Jake Browning's pass is tipped and intercepted by Josh Sandry, who returns it 35 yards for a touchdown.

videos.headline: Washington's Gaskin finds end zone untouched
videos.description: Huskies RB Myles Gaskin easily scores from four yards out to give Washington the 14-7 lead.

videos.headline: Huskies' Pettis breaks Pac-12 career punt return TD record
videos.description: Dante Pettis breaks the Pac-12 Conference record for career punt return touchdowns with a scintillating, tackle-breaking 67-yard return.

videos.headline: Coleman pounds it in for Washington TD
videos.description: Huskies' RB Lavon Coleman runs it up the gut and scores a 4-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Browning finds Dissly for Huskies TD
videos.description: Huskies QB Jake Browning connects with Will Dissly for a 20-yard touchdown, giving Washington the 35-7 lead at halftime.

videos.headline: UW defender rips ball away from receiver for INT
videos.description: Washington's Sean Constantine records his first career interception by taking the ball straight from the Montana receiver's hands.

videos.headline: Browning finds a wide-open Dissly for another TD
videos.description: Washington QB Jake Browning buys time in the pocket and connects with Will Dissly for a 3-yard TD.

videos.headline: Washington returns INT 68 yards to the house
videos.description: Jomon Dotson picks off Montana's pass and returns it 68 yards for a touchdown.

videos.headline: Freshman RB scores Huskies' 8th TD of day
videos.description: Washington freshman RB Salvon Ahmed scores untouched from 1 yard out for his first career touchdown.

videos.headline: Huskies' McGrew scores first career TD
videos.description: Washington freshman Sean McGrew runs it in from 3 yards out to put Washington up 63-7.
